  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether midodrine administration decreases duration
      of intravenous vasopressors and intensive care unit length of stay for patients in septic
      shock.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Withdrawn</overall_status>
  <why_stopped>
